token_info.name: Forest Spirit - ED
token_info.description: Among my friends there are extraordinary people, those who live in full force, burn like a big fire and attract others to their projects and deeds. These are the people of the Giants, the Heroes of our time. One of such people is Eduard Yasaveev, a forest spirit, a conductor of sound and the creator of @Dzin.Space A flaming bonfire that rushes forward and upward.  I dedicate this sculpture to him, with gratitude and respect for everything he does.
